<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TKT14">
<l>kāviyai veṉṟa kaṇṇār kalaviyē karuti nāḷum</l>
<l>pāviyē ṉāka veṇṇi yataṉuḷḷē paḻutto ḻintēṉ</l>
<l>tūvicē raṉṉam maṉṉuñ cūḻpuṉal kuṭantai yāṉai</l>
<l>pāviyēṉ pāvi yātu pāviyē ṉāyi ṉēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Daily thinking only of the embraces of ladies [whose] eyes rivaled dark lilies,</l>
<l>As the sinner that I am, pondering, I remained rotting in it.</l>
<l>I, a sinner, became a sinner [by] not contemplate him</l>
<l>Of Kuṭantai where downy swans stay in the surrounding floods.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
